  Temperature &
  High &
  \begin{tabular}[c]{@{}l@{}}Higher Temperature\end{tabular} &
  \begin{tabular}[c]{@{}l@{}}Metabolic heat buildup {[}1{]}\\ \\Formation of cell lumps in\\ the bioreactor {[}1{]}\\ \\Non-homogeneous heat \\creation by the cells {[}1{]}\\ \\Controller malfunction\\ \\Faulty sensor\\ \\Bioreactor malfunction\\ \\Medium heater malfunction\\ \\Temperature wrongly set to\\cleaning and sterilization \\temperature \\(higher than 70 C)\end{tabular} &
  
  \begin{tabular}[c]{@{}l@{}}Increased heat stress\\on the cells\\ \\Reduced proliferation\\ \\Activation of the cell\\heat shock response\\that alters the DNA and\\ structure of the cells {[}3{]}\\ \\Higher risk of \\apoptosis (cell death)\\ and development of\\necrotic tissue\\ \\Reactor overheat\end{tabular} &
  
  \begin{tabular}[c]{@{}l@{}}Add a jacket to the bioreactor\\to control the temperature\\ \\Implement alarm systems to\\alert operators when the\\temperature is outside of the\\desired range (36-41 C) {[}2{]}***\\ \\Have emergency shutdown \\procedures in place and\\manual override systems\\ for excessive temperatures\\ \\Develop cooling mechanisms \\to reduce the temperature \\(preferably passive cooling \\systems to decrease the \\environmental impact {[}1{]})\\ \\Use multiple sensors\\ to ensure accurate readings\\ \\Have emergency shutdown \\procedures and manual \\override systems in place\end{tabular} \\ \hline

